> DANG!!!!!!!! I hear the slamming of a cell door. <br />
> *Hoo-Hoo*?? sealed shut! <br />
> Butt?? Sealed shut! <br />
> I penguin walk around the bathroom trying to figure out what to do and think <br />
> to myself "Please don't let me get the urge to poop. <br />
> My head may pop off!" <br />
> What can I do to melt the wax? Hot water!! Hot water melts wax!!! <br />
